<p><b>A WEEKLY TIP ON CARING FOR OUR COMMON HOME</b>.
Consider planting trees and/or shrubs next to your
house. They will help keep you cool naturally in
warmer weather, and they help to pull carbon from the
atmosphere.</p>


<p><b>INTENTIONAL SERVICE AND WELCOMING SPIRITUAL
