meet regularly in community to deepen their
spirituality and explore the values of community,
simple living and social and ecological justice. Priority
application deadline: August 15. <i>Information</i>,
<a target="_bulletin" href="mailto:JVESeattle@jvcnorthwest.org">JVESeattle@jvcnorthwest.org</a> or 
<a target="_bulletin" href="http://www.jvencorps.org">www.jvencorps.org</a>.</p>


